The paper deals with deep learning and classification tasks, which are typically associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of prior knowledge in the form of class hierarchies, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper mentions experiments on image datasets, which could also be associated with multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
